### ping api (使用Cookie认证)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ping
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

{
  "message": "hello"
}

### get credits
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/credits
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

### gen image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/gen-image
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "prompt": "a beautiful girl running with 2 cats",
  "provider": "kling",
  "model": "kling-v1"
}

### gen video
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/gen-video
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "a beautiful girl running with 2 cats",
  "provider": "kling",
  "model": "kling-v1-6"
}

### prompt优化 - 测试1: 纯文字优化（向后兼容）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/optimize-prompt
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

{
  "videoGenerationId": "057a488c-c5fc-4f53-97b7-6e98b7e41410",
  "originalPrompt": "一只可爱的小猫在花园里玩耍"
}

### prompt优化 - 测试2: 文字+图片多模态优化（阿里云 Qwen-VL）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/optimize-prompt
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

{
  "videoGenerationId": "057a488c-c5fc-4f53-97b7-6e98b7e41410",
  "originalPrompt": "美丽的日落风景，天空中有云朵",
  "imageUrl": "https://picsum.photos/id/1018/800/600"
}

